    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've been abducted by aliens... and put to work!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Have fun with physics!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pull, tug, bounce and throw around all kinds of aliens, gadgets, and thingamajigs! (almost) Everything is interactable!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/49ea636e067557a78049ea302792de40.poster.avif?t=1771521940\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/49ea636e067557a78049ea302792de40.webm?t=1771521940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/49ea636e067557a78049ea302792de40.mp4?t=1771521940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weird jobs in a unique episodic narrative!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abduct new recruits in the Abductorium, take care of alien babies at the Daycare and cook up some questionable space snacks at the GlorpoVision Music festival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/9967547eb9b25db488779a74ec5cef4c.poster.avif?t=1771521940\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/9967547eb9b25db488779a74ec5cef4c.webm?t=1771521940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/9967547eb9b25db488779a74ec5cef4c.mp4?t=1771521940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meet your alien crew!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go on wild adventures with Melody, Widgett and Zorgle - Your friendly space companions on this corporate adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/d5a52dc978ff4db1998e05f711ba1c57.poster.avif?t=1771521940\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/d5a52dc978ff4db1998e05f711ba1c57.webm?t=1771521940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/d5a52dc978ff4db1998e05f711ba1c57.mp4?t=1771521940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An immersive, whimsically dystopian world!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy cartoony environments inspired by the absurdity of beloved shows like Futurama and Rick&amp;Morty!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/b2afb489c9394e10e85bb889a878a2e6.poster.avif?t=1771521940\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/b2afb489c9394e10e85bb889a878a2e6.webm?t=1771521940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759150/extras/b2afb489c9394e10e85bb889a878a2e6.mp4?t=1771521940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
